    "title": "FaultSystem",
    "description": "DEPRECATED: use the SeismicFault or GenericRepresentation WPCs instead. These are representations of an individual fault. The grouping of individual faults can be achieved through the UnsealedSurfaceFramework or Persisted Collection WPCs. ~~A set of picked faults. In the earth modeling domain this entity corresponds to a PersistedCollection containing GenericRepresentation or SeismicFault items.~~",
    "type": "object",
